{"text_id":196527,"tokens":["The"," Electoral"," College"," is"," a"," system"," established"," by"," the"," United"," States"," Constitution"," to"," elect"," the"," President"," and"," Vice"," President"," of"," the"," United"," States","."," It"," is"," a"," process"," that"," occurs"," every"," four"," years",","," in"," which"," voters"," cast"," their"," ballots"," for"," presidential"," and"," vice","-","pres","idential"," candidates",","," who"," are"," elected"," through"," a"," separate"," process","."," ","\n\n","The"," system"," has"," long"," been"," controversial"," due"," to"," its"," inherent"," flaws"," and"," lack"," of"," representation","."," One"," major"," flaw"," is"," that"," it"," does"," not"," always"," reflect"," the"," will"," of"," the"," people","."," The"," Electoral"," College"," awards"," votes"," to"," states"," based"," on"," their"," total"," number"," of"," representatives"," in"," Congress",","," meaning"," that"," less"," populous"," states"," have"," more"," influence"," per"," voter"," than"," more"," populous"," ones","."," This"," is"," problematic"," because"," it"," gives"," less"," representation"," to"," voters"," in"," more"," populated"," states",","," who"," ultimately"," have"," no"," vote"," in"," the"," college",".","\n\n","Another"," issue"," is"," the"," possibility"," of"," election"," fraud"," or"," error","."," In"," the"," Electoral"," College"," system",","," individual"," states"," are"," responsible"," for"," conducting"," elections"," and"," reporting"," results"," to"," the"," federal"," government","."," This"," leaves"," the"," system"," vulnerable"," to"," errors"," or"," fraudulent"," activities"," that"," could"," alter"," the"," outcome"," of"," the"," election"," at"," the"," state"," level",".","\n\n","A"," direct"," election"," system",","," in"," which"," voters"," cast"," ballots"," for"," presidential"," and"," vice","-","pres","idential"," candidates",","," would"," be"," a"," more"," democratic"," alternative"," to"," the"," Electoral"," College","."," Under"," this"," system",","," every"," vote"," would"," have"," equal"," weight",","," regardless"," of"," where"," it"," is"," cast",","," ensuring"," that"," the"," will"," of"," the"," people"," is"," accurately"," represented","."," This"," would"," help"," to"," address"," the"," issue"," of"," voter"," inequality"," and"," would"," be"," more"," straightforward"," and"," less"," subject"," to"," fraud"," or"," error","."," ","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," is"," flawed"," and"," controversial"," because"," it"," does"," not"," always"," reflect"," the"," will"," of"," the"," people"," and"," is"," vulnerable"," to"," errors"," and"," fraud","."," Therefore",","," a"," direct"," election"," system"," should"," be"," adopted"," in"," its"," place"," to"," ensure"," every"," voter"," is"," represented"," equally","."," ","\n\n","Would"," you"," like"," help"," with"," anything"," else"," regarding"," problem"," statements"," and"," essays","?"],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"cohere","label":1}